<h2>Create New Game</h2>

<div style="background: #e9ecef; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
  <h3>How to Play Turing Twist</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>5-8 players join the game (2 will always be AI)</li>
    <li>Each round, everyone answers a personal question</li>
    <li>Read all answers and vote for who you think is the AI</li>
    <li>The player with the most votes is eliminated</li>
    <li>Continue until all AIs are found (humans win) or AIs survive (AIs win)</li>
  </ol>
</div>

<%= form_with model: @game, local: true do |f| %>
  <p>Click the button below to create a new game. The game will start automatically when enough players join.</p>

  <%= f.submit "Create Game", style: "background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.1rem;" %>
<% end %>

<%= link_to "Back to Games", games_path, style: "display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; color: #007bff;" %>